== 評價 ==
该片获得了极大的好评，在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]网站，它获得了97%的新鲜度；知名影评人[[Vincent_Canby|Vincent Canby]]评论道“它是Sidney Lumet最精确，最耀眼的关于纽约的电影”，并对全部演员赞扬道“他们都塑造了杰出的人物”(brilliant characterizations)<ref>[http://movies2.nytimes.com/mem/movies/review.html?title1=&title2=Dog%20Day%20Afternoon%20%28Movie%29&reviewer=VINCENT%20CANBY&v_id=14193 Screen: Lumet's ''Dog Day Afternoon''] {{Wayback|url=http://movies2.nytimes.com/mem/movies/review.html?title1=&title2=Dog%20Day%20Afternoon%20%28Movie%29&reviewer=VINCENT%20CANBY&v_id=14193 |date=20170305002529 }} by Vincent Camby for The New York Times on September 22, 1975. Retrieved June 3, 2006.</ref>；[[Roger_Ebert|Roger Ebert]]评价说Sonny是“最有趣的一个现代电影角色”，并给予影片三星半(满分四星)的打分<ref>[http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/19750101/REVIEWS/501010313/1023 ''Dog Day Afternoon''] {{Wayback|url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F19750101%2FREVIEWS%2F501010313%2F1023 |date=20120910074915 }} by Roger Ebert for the Chicago Sun-Times on January 1, 1975. Retrieved June 3, 2006.</ref>。

